OL,3,CBrothers sentenced over #3.2m tax scam
OL,5,FTwo property developer brothers have
OL,6,Fbeen sentenced over a #3.2million tax
OL,7,Fscam.
OL,9,FStephen Hirst, 62, from Bridlington,
OL,10,Fand Michael Hirst, 55, from Wakefield,
OL,11,Fused offshore companies in overseas
OL,12,Fterritories to hide money from the
OL,13,Fsale of land in Wakefield.
OL,15,FThey pleaded guilty to cheating the
OL,16,Fpublic revenue in July 2023, but were
OL,17,Fgiven a year to pay both the tax they
OL,18,Fowed and the prosecution costs.
