OL,3,CBrothers sentenced over #3.2m tax scam
OL,5,FHaving paid the amounts owed they were
OL,6,Feach sentenced at Leeds Crown Court to
OL,7,Ftwo years in prison, suspended for two
OL,8,Fyears.
OL,10,FStephen Hirst was fined #12,000.
OL,11,FMichael Hirst was fined #8,000.
OL,13,FBoth men have been banned from acting
OL,14,Fas company directors for eight years.
OL,16,FThe case dated back to August 1999,
OL,17,Fwhen the brothers' company Heritage
OL,18,FHoldings Limited bought land on Park
OL,19,FDrive in Wakefield for just over
OL,20,F#700,000.
