OL,3,CBrothers sentenced over #3.2m tax scam
OL,5,FThe brothers split the plot into four
OL,6,Fparts and sold some of it for much
OL,7,Fless than it was worth to a second
OL,8,Fcompany, registered in Gibraltar but
OL,9,Frun by the defendants in the UK.
OL,11,FThey also set up another company of
OL,12,Fthe same name in the British Virgin
OL,13,FIslands.
OL,15,FIn March 2007, the land was sold for
OL,16,Fover #10million after planning
OL,17,Fpermission was granted.
