OL,3,CBrothers sentenced over #3.2m tax scam
OL,5,F"Instead, they lied about the network
OL,6,Fof firms and ownership structures they
OL,7,Fhad set up to commit fraud and have
OL,8,Fended up with criminal convictions,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,F"We are pleased to have recovered
OL,12,Fevery penny of the money they stole,
OL,13,Fwhich will now be used on the public
OL,14,Fservices we all rely on.
OL,16,F"We continue to work tirelessly to
OL,17,Fensure the tax system is fair to all
OL,18,Fand this case shows once again that we
OL,19,Fwill work with international partners
OL,20,Fto ensure a level playing for all
OL,21,Ftaxpayers."
